data.description: Here's your opportunity to nestle into the Hillside! Arctic entry leads to open living space with vaulted ceilings and ample windows to let the sunshine in, wood stove for extra-efficient warmth plus kitchen w/gas range and picture window. Basement with 3rd bedroom, full bath, sauna, laundry & lots of storage space, fenced back yard & a large front yardwith pergola deck for enjoying the sunhine. 4* energy rated. Assumable VA loand with 3.125% interest rate.
